  "directions": [
    "In Crock-Pot, combine water, cream soda, sugar, butter, 1/4 cup butterscotch, cinnamon sticks, vanilla and salt.",
    "Cover and cook on low for 3 to 3 1/2 hours, until warm and butter is melted. Remove lid and stir in rum.",
    "Pour remaining butterscotch syrup onto a shallow plate.",
    "Dip rims of mugs in syrup before filling with butter beer.",
    "Top with whipped cream, sprinkle with sanding sugar, and serve."
